body.raw:
Actor, playwright, and award-winning musician living and working outside *Boston, MA*. Leftist; deeply invested in theatre as a medium for social change. Entertainment is *overrated*.

Want to reach out? Find me on Twitter *@thejessewinton*, or email me at *hi@jessewinton.com*.
